attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene -

data.description: Beautifully renovated home on a corner lot with loads of extras! Gorgeous and easy-to-maintain wood look tile floors throughout downstairs living areas. Step into the stunning living room with 2-story ceilings, floor to ceiling fireplace, double french door access to outside, and a dry bar with a wine fridge! Spacious formal dining room gives way to the bright and updated kitchen with quartz counters, tile backsplash, upgraded SS appliances, built-in desk space, and breakfast room. Retreat to the oversized downstairs primary bedroom with plantation shutters and outside access as well as an updated en-suite bath with dual sinks, vanity seating, soaking tub, and unique tile finishes! Upstairs, enjoy a game room with built-ins and multiple seating areas, as well as two more spacious secondary bedrooms with a jack-and-jill bathroom. Don't miss the fully fenced backyard with a huge patio slab and mature trees!
